description: You're home in this chic, sun-filled penthouse house condo. Converted in 2008, this three-unit building is well located in the heart of City Point within steps of the South Boston beaches, the Broadway shops, and Castle Island...Across the threshold, this one-bedroom unit has a loft-like feel, with soaring cathedral ceilings. The working kitchen has granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and cherry cabinets. Other amenities/details include a large bedroom with lots of closet space, an oversized jacuzzi bath, in-unit laundry, a storage unit, and a private deck perfect for entertaining on a nice summer day. This is a great entry-level unit!
